Starting my day slow & feeling my best ✨💆‍♀️

Mornings lately have been all about simple rituals that help me feel refreshed and reset:

🥤 supergreen Bloom to start the day right
🚿 long shower with Tree Hut scrub (so satisfying)
🥥 moisturizing with coconut oil for soft, glowy skin
🧊 face roller + mask for the ultimate de-puff
📖 a good book to set the vibe

Taking care of yourself doesn’t have to be complicated. It’s the little things—sticking to habits that make you feel good, moving at your own pace, and actually enjoying your mornings instead of rushing through them.
